These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, train, scooter
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, begonia, aconite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, swisher, ritmeester, blend
 1. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person driving the scooter##6
 5. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
 6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is not the blend-smoker##6
 9. the person driving the motorbike is not the person who growsaconite##6
10. the swisher-smoker is the person who growsaconite##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
13. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
14. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Transport    | motorbike         | scooter     | train     | snowmobile         |
| Flower   | bellflower | aconite    | begonia     | amaryllis |
| Cigar   | pall-mall       | swisher | blend | ritmeester       |

