.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, train, bus
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, blood-red, chestnut, black
There 4 different types of food: busmelon, cranberry, lime, corn
 1. the person who likes chestnut is not to the right of the person who likes black##8
 2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating busmelon##1
 4. the person driving the bus is the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is not the person driving the train##6
 6. the person eating busmelon is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
10. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Transport   | train          | trike      | bus      | jet-ski   |
| Color        | chestnut     | apricot | blood-red | black      |
| Food      | corn | cranberry    | busmelon  | lime |

