.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, pink, white, lilac
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing, sailing, water-polo
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, snooker, bridge
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 5. the person playing monopoly is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 8. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Color         | white  | pink | lilac | ebony |
| Sport   | surfing  | snowboarding      | water-polo | sailing        |
| Game     | monopoly | snooker       | bridge    | billiard     |

