.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, bird, ferret
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, juice, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, oliveros, baccarat, prince
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the oliveros-smoker##8
 6. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
 7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 8. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the owner of the ferret is the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Pet   | rabbit   | ferret | fish    | bird |
| Beverage   | juice    | fanta     | hot-chocolate   | water     |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | baccarat   | oliveros | prince    |

