4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, guinea-pig, frog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, mirinda, coffee
 1. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 4. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the frog is not the alhambra-smoker##6
 7. the havana-smoker is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 8. the owner of the bird is the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
10. the person drinking coffee is the alhambra-smoker##1
11. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar         | alhambra       | havana | oliveros  | blend    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig       | frog    | bird | hamster    |
| Beverage         | coffee | lemonade   | mirinda   | tea |

