The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, november, april
City: liverpool, berlin, london, new-york
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person traveling to berlin##6
 3. the person traveling to london is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the person who's birthday is in april##7
 4. the person traveling to berlin is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
 6. the person traveling to london is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 8. the person traveling to new-york is between the montecristo-smoker and the person traveling to london##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
10. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
11. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Cigar          | alhambra      | ritmeester      | swisher | montecristo |
| Birthday   | november | march    | april | december     |
| City   | liverpool    | london | new-york  | berlin |

