 4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person playing poker is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
 8. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
10. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
11. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
12. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
13. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5

