.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lilac, apricot, azure
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, zinnia, rose
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, november, august
1. the person who growstulip is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsrose##2
4. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who likes lilac is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in december##7
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Color   | lilac | red     | azure  | apricot |
| Flower           | daisy      | rose        | zinnia   | tulip |
| Birthday         | december  | november | august | may       |

 